                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 816.001Ar1/3.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President of Salvador</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">President</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">San Salvador</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-02-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 7, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I sincerely thank you for your kind message and send Your Excellency my best
                    thanks for your expression of sympathy in the criminal attempt. Out of danger. I
                    assure you of my friendship.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Presidente Araújo</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
